         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne Botanic Garden, ¶ 15 February 1872. ¶  ¶ Today, noble friend, and just as the mail is leaving, the news arrived here that the graciousness of your august King has admitted me into the Order ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">72.02.15a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Jacob Agardh</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Handskr. Avdl., Universitetsbibliotek, Lund, Sweden.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS bears a letterhead of M's proposed baronial coat of arms. Agardh acknowledged receipt of M’s letter in J. Agardh to M, July 1872 (in this edition as 72-07-00a).</p>
               </note>Melbourne, im bot Garten,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">15/2/72</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>An diesem Tage, edler Freund, u. gerade beim Postabgang trifft die Zuschrift hier ein, durch welche die Gnade Ihres hehren Königs mich in den Orden des Nordsterns aufnimmt. Diese <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">hohe</hi>
               </seg> Ehrenbezeugung, welche ich sicher Ihrer Fürsprache verdanke, hat mich sehr gerührt, und ich lege besonders hohen Werth darauf, da ja Linné diesen Orden ebenfalls trug.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Es bleibt mir keine Zeit die Zuschfrift Sr. Excellenz des Ordens-Kanzlers diesmal zu beantworten, u. so muss ich den Ausspruch meines Dankes bis zur nächsten Post verschieben</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mag die Vorsehung mir Kraft u Gesundheit verleihen, um mich <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">dankbar</hi>
               </seg> zu bezeigen.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Hoffentlich kamen die Baumfarne lebend an. — Sollte dies unglücklicher Weise nicht der Fall gewesen sein, so werde ich eine <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">neue</hi>
               </seg> Zusendung veranstalten. Ich habe Ihnen doch noch eine riesige <name key="Todea">Todea</name> zu senden.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mit besonderer Dankbarkeit der Ihre</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne Botanic Garden,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">15 February 1872.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Today, noble friend, and just as the mail is leaving, the news arrived here that the graciousness of your august King has admitted me into the Order of the North Star.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See Carl XV, King of Sweden and Norway, to M, 9 December 1871 (in this ediion as 71-12-09a).</p>
               </note> This <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">high</hi>
               </seg> distinction, which I surely owe to your intercession, has touched me deeply, and I particularly value it because Linnaeus also wore this Order.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>There is no time left to reply to the letter from His Excellency, the Chancellor of the Order, so I must delay the expression of my gratitude until the next mail.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>May Providence give me strength and health to prove my <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">gratitude</hi>
               </seg>.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I hope the tree ferns arrived alive.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">M shipped 7 trunks of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Dicksonia antarctica</seg> to Agardh by <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Anglesey</seg>; see M to J. Agardh, 15 July 1871 and 25 July 1871.</p>
               </note> If by misfortune that should not be the case, I shall organize a <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">new</hi>
               </seg> sending. I still have to send you a giant <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Todea">Todea</name>
               </seg>.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With particular gratitude, your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Todea">Todea</name>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
